				<outline text="The vision of using GitHub to host users data that could be accessed by lots of apps, a planned community of  apps that autormatically interop, where users fully own their data, will have to wait until we better understand how &lt;a href=&quot;http://scripting.com/2021/06/23/174309.html?title=isGithubRawStorageReliable&quot;&gt;GitHub works&lt;/a&gt; with raw data." created="Wed, 23 Jun 2021 22:14:40 GMT" type="outline"/>
